text: Upama Kumari Dev (Nepali: उपमा कुमारी देव) is a Nepalese politician who is elected member of Provincial Assembly of Madhesh Province from People's Socialist Party, Nepal. Dev is a resident of Rajbiraj.She is also a Deputy Speaker of Provincial Assembly of Madhesh Province, took office on 16 February 2018. == References == Category:Living people Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Upama Kumari Dev
